1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:46,780
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:46,820 --> 00:00:48,820
=Episode 13=
=Niannian's Fury & Lang's Confession=

11
00:01:08,590 --> 00:01:09,430
Ye Lang.

12
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:10,680
Finally!

13
00:01:14,260 --> 00:01:16,540
(If you want to see Jiang Xiaodi,
come here.)

14
00:01:41,380 --> 00:01:43,500
(Renxin Hospital)

15
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,920
Renxin Hospital.

16
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,070
Ye Lang's car.

17
00:01:57,710 --> 00:01:58,550
No.

18
00:01:59,040 --> 00:01:59,880
No way.

19
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,520
Jiang Niannian.

20
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:06,960
Calm down.

21
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:09,080
When you find Xiaodi,

22
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,000
the truth will come out.

23
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:42,420
(In Surgery)

24
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,840
How is it?

25
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,640
Don't worry.

26
00:02:48,910 --> 00:02:49,870
How is it?

27
00:02:50,470 --> 00:02:51,520
Let me wash my hands first.

28
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,240
(Ye Lang.)

29
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,000
(Really him.)

30
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,360
(Xiaodi.)

31
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:01,150
(Where is Xiaodi?)

32
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:02,960
(No.)

33
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:04,550
(That's impossible.)

34
00:03:05,590 --> 00:03:07,080
The blood bank got units here in time.

35
00:03:07,310 --> 00:03:08,470
Luckily you arrived in time.

36
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:11,080
(Blood bank?)

37
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,080
(Luckily?)

38
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,470
Being a match for Xiaodi

39
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:16,400
is incredibly rare.

40
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,280
The surgery went well.

41
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,470
(A successful match?)

42
00:03:20,820 --> 00:03:22,470
After hiding it from Niannian for so long,

43
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,840
we can finally give her a healthy brother.

44
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:27,800
(Hiding it from me...)

45
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,120
You did a lot.

46
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:32,080
We need to monitor his post-op condition.

47
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:33,550
(You did a lot...)

48
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,080
(Post-op condition.)

49
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:37,560
Alas.

50
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,520
Finally, no more lies to Jiang Niannian.

51
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,200
You okay?

52
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,470
I feel dizzy and nauseous.

53
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:50,000
Maybe you gave too much blood.

54
00:03:50,590 --> 00:03:51,680
(Lies.)

55
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:53,870
(Nauseous.)

56
00:04:01,750 --> 00:04:03,150
(It really was him.)

57
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,430
(He's the one who hid Xiaodi.)

58
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,310
(Those sweet words,)

59
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,190
(that true love,)

60
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,750
(all lies.)

61
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,000
(All of it was for today.)

62
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,950
(I was stupid enough to believe)

63
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:34,790
(that in this world,)

64
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:37,070
(someone could love me completely.)

65
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,270
(I even sent my own brother)

66
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:42,070
(straight into hell myself.)

67
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:09,880
Who are you?

68
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:10,790
Why are you here?

69
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,320
Jiang Niannian.

70
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,400
Why are you here?

71
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:36,830
Jiang Niannian.

72
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,350
Are you insane?

73
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,240
I am.

74
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,270
I'll kill you right now.

75
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:46,040
Go join Xiaodi!

76
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:48,670
(This moment)

77
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,240
(has finally come.)

78
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,830
If Xiaodi is dead,

79
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,680
then go to hell too.

80
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,320
(Why?)

81
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:04,480
(Why has nothing changed?)

82
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:07,750
(Is this always how we end?)

83
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,560
Niannian.

84
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:14,240
Listen to me.

85
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,120
Someone, get blood!

86
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,080
Prepare the OR!

87
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:24,510
Ventricular fibrillation!

88
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:25,680
Push lidocaine, now!

89
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,520
No blood pressure!

90
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:27,670
Defibrillation!

91
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,270
Stay calm, 1mg epinephrine IV!

92
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,430
Another shock!

93
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,440
Why?

94
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:43,070
Why did the blade go in,

95
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,120
and I still couldn't end him?

96
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,600
Why can't I bring myself to do it?

97
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:04,390
(Nurses' Station)
Move!

98
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:05,230
Out of the way!

99
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,400
Wait.

100
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,000
Go check on Jiang Niannian.

101
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:14,680
Don't let her do anything rash.

102
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,510
Bro, at a time like this?

103
00:07:16,770 --> 00:07:18,630
If he dies,
send the body to me for dissection.

104
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,000
Xiaodi.

105
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:54,800
This is all my fault.

106
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,680
I'm coming to be with you now.

107
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,880
Jiang Niannian!

108
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:08,960
Snap out of it!

109
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:09,960
Xiaodi isn't dead.

110
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,840
Look.

111
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,720
His brain tumor pressed a vessel

112
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,030
and caused bleeding.

113
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,600
We got no enough O-type RH-negative blood.

114
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,240
Even with emergency transfers,

115
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:49,470
it wasn't enough.

116
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:50,910
That's why I called

117
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,840
Ye Lang here.

118
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,200
He drew blood himself,

119
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:56,440
and hold on till your brother's safe.

120
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,030
Really silly.

121
00:08:59,030 --> 00:09:01,040
If anything happens to him,
you owe me a new heart.

122
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:29,940
(Admission Time, Treating Doctor)

123
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:31,340
(Zheng Lu)

124
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:36,060
(Jiang Xiaodi, Admission Time)

125
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,670
After my brother disappeared,

126
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,550
he's been in this hospital?

127
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:48,030
So from the very start,

128
00:09:48,510 --> 00:09:50,510
my brother was under your watch.

129
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,200
That's right.

130
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:53,990
That idiot

131
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,270
said someone wanted

132
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:56,230
to kill Xiaodi,

133
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:57,870
but he didn't know who it was.

134
00:09:58,670 --> 00:09:59,840
He said he'd be safe here,

135
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:00,960
and couldn't leave.

136
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,480
And you two couldn't meet.

137
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,120
Can you give me Ye Lang's phone?

138
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,750
I need his key

139
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,750
to confirm something.

140
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,040
Okay.

141
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:15,040
(Nurses' Station)

142
00:10:24,660 --> 00:10:28,660
(Behave and Jiang Xiaodi will be fine.)

143
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:33,630
It turns out he sent those emails.

144
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,030
And I stupidly thought

145
00:10:36,790 --> 00:10:38,320
someone was using me to hurt him.

146
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:42,790
How ridiculous.

147
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:51,990
Three million.

148
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:53,790
You have to follow the rules.

149
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:03,440
Marry the dead?

150
00:11:05,750 --> 00:11:06,610
What's the issue?

151
00:11:06,630 --> 00:11:07,470
No, no issue.

152
00:11:07,470 --> 00:11:08,320
I'll go now.

153
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:10,870
Jiang Niannian was born tough.

154
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,270
Your family picked her,

155
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,510
that's her good luck.

156
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:14,360
Yes.

157
00:11:14,390 --> 00:11:15,840
Niannian's been smart since little.

158
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:17,680
She is sensible,
and won't go back on it.

159
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:29,780
(Renxin Hospital, Outpatient Hall)

160
00:11:35,260 --> 00:11:38,820
(One Week Later)

161
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:40,920
Niannian.

162
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:45,080
How did you get hurt?

163
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:45,920
Three months ago,

164
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:49,000
you went to Jiang Feng and Liu Qin

165
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:52,390
and had them sign the contract to marry me.

166
00:11:57,030 --> 00:11:58,030
And that same day,

167
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,550
you secretly moved my brother

168
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:02,720
and checked his blood type thoroughly.

169
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:04,840
This was all your setup!

170
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:07,590
Ye Lang.

171
00:12:08,550 --> 00:12:10,550
You plotted this whole thing.

172
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,840
No!

173
00:12:21,390 --> 00:12:22,230
I...

174
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,320
Actually,

175
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:27,120
I was reborn.

176
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:37,200
In the past, Zheng Lu died in a crash.

177
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:40,030
Later, Xiaodi died on the operating table.

178
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:41,350
And I...

179
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,510
I died at our wedding too.

180
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:48,140
♪For your return♪

181
00:12:49,790 --> 00:12:50,630
Ye Lang,

182
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:53,030
you're making things up again.

183
00:12:55,870 --> 00:12:57,240
Why not say you're an alien?

184
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,510
I know this is hard to explain.

185
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:06,000
But hear me out.

186
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:08,360
I was only in a coma for a week,

187
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,080
but you can ask me

188
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,550
everything that happened

189
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:12,600
during that one week.

190
00:13:14,910 --> 00:13:15,750
Ye Lang,

191
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:17,390
you're lying to me again.

192
00:13:19,980 --> 00:13:21,530
♪I can't stand♪

193
00:13:22,350 --> 00:13:23,580
♪So, I'll give in♪

194
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,960
I know you won't believe me now.

195
00:13:26,750 --> 00:13:27,750
But I'm begging you...

196
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:29,980
♪Why can't you stay?♪

197
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,600
Please, just wait till tomorrow.

198
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,600
It'll snow tomorrow.

199
00:13:36,390 --> 00:13:38,000
If it doesn't,

200
00:13:38,810 --> 00:13:39,670
I swear,

201
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:42,200
I'll never show up again.

202
00:13:42,430 --> 00:13:44,420
♪I cannot hear you♪

203
00:13:46,150 --> 00:13:47,120
It's June right now.

204
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:49,870
Check the forecast before lying.

205
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:53,440
I'm grateful you saved Xiaodi,

206
00:13:53,870 --> 00:13:54,720
but right now,

207
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,960
I don't believe a word you say.

208
00:13:56,720 --> 00:14:00,850
♪Where did you go?♪

209
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:32,790
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

210
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:40,810
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

211
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:48,360
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

212
00:14:49,110 --> 00:14:51,580
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

213
00:14:51,580 --> 00:14:56,580
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

214
00:14:56,580 --> 00:15:00,810
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

215
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:05,250
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

216
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:09,090
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

217
00:15:09,090 --> 00:15:14,840
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

218
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:19,160
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

219
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:23,020
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

220
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:27,520
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

221
00:15:27,550 --> 00:15:32,380
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

222
00:15:32,780 --> 00:15:39,320
♪Life finds its way again♪

